cc:Work.dc:title: Apollo Moon Landing
cc:Work.dc:description: This is based on a publicity image published a few months before the moon landing by nasa in 1969 (as a US government institution, their works are in the public domain). The image is a bit like a sketch, but it captures the artist's imagination of this historic event. (I had to touch it up as best I could, added a few details that were missing--- I didn't do the best job, but I hope this helps some people!)
